general_info: From business cards to billboards, email signatures to web banner ads and from websites to email marketing We do it all and everything in-between. Bring REM Interactive your marketing challenges and let us provide you with professional looking custom graphic design solutions for any sized project. Our commitment to our clients has helped us build an impressive portfolio spanning many different industries, products and services. We've been this successful over the years for one basic reason: we help our clients be more successful. It's as simple as that. Let Us be Your Creative Department! REM Interactive specializes in working with companies and individuals to meet all their marketing and creative needs - on the web, in print, in apps, you name it - and we've become really good at doing it as quickly and efficiently as if we were in-house. We believe that if "you can think of it, we can create it for you". This is how our tagline came into existence. The sleep cycle identified as REM (rapid eye movement) is a time when the brain shows increased activity and when the most vivid and symbolic dreams occur. Some people believe that these are goal oriented dreams and others that they are conflict resolution processes. Regardless of these two concepts, REM Interactive believes that the flood of images and symbols that occur in the sleeper's mind can be copied by a flowing exchange with a client. Whether an idea is very clear in their head or just a rough concept, we take these ideas and turn them into working solutions.If you're looking to establish an online presence, we can build a very professional, yet simple and informative type of website. If your preference is to have an industry leading portal type site with traffic driving SEO strategies in place, we can do that for you as well.
